Global setup:
 Set up git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email bhattsachin@gmail.com
      
Next steps:
  mkdir SpringMVCMongoDB
  cd SpringMVCMongoDB
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin https://github.com/bhattsachin/SpringMVCMongoDB.git
  git push -u origin master
      
Existing Git Repo?
  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin https://github.com/bhattsachin/SpringMVCMongoDB.git
  git push -u origin master

Also have an instance of Mongodb running on localhost

use [database];
db.dropDatabase()